{{version030}}
{{flavour|It causes witnesses of the wearer's kills to go into a frenzy, attacking everything nearby with great strength and speed.}}

'''Mayhem''' is an [[ego]] found only on [[orb]]s. Characters wielding an orb of mayhem have a 50% chance of inflicting [[frenzy]] on another monster whenever they kill a foe. Frenzied monsters are [[neutral]], attack the closest thing (friend or foe), and gain immense power and speed ([[might]] and [[haste]]).

==Strategy==
*Mayhem is most useful in areas you know will be filled with monsters; areas like [[Vaults]]:5 or a [[Ziggurat]].
*Whilst very powerful when fighting a group, be aware that it can backfire. For example, it can frenzy your own [[summon]]s, or enrage the only enemy left alive.
**There are a few ways to deal with dangerous frenzied monsters that target you. [[Spriggan]]s can easily outrun even hasted monsters, other characters can [[teleport]] away, and you can dispel frenzy with [[Yara's Violent Unravelling]] or a [[wand of quicksilver]].

==History==
The mayhem ego, along with orbs themselves, was introduced in [[0.28]].

